keyFacts: The Nine East 71st Street Corporation was incorporated on August 25, 1989.
Jeffrey E. Epstein served as the President of the corporation.
Darren K. Indyke served as the Secretary and attorney for the corporation.
The corporation was dissolved in December 2012 by unanimous consent.
The New York State Department of Taxation and Finance consented to the dissolution on April 29, 2015.
